OL,3,CDeath recorded in England linked to
OL,4,Congoing E.coli outbreak, UKHSA says
OL,6,FThe source of the outbreak has been
OL,7,Flinked back to contaminated lettuce
OL,8,Fleaves, as ITV News' Science
OL,9,FCorrespondent Martin Stew explains.
OL,11,FOne person in England has died linked
OL,12,Fto the ongoing E.coli outbreak, the UK
OL,13,FHealth Security Agency (UKHSA) has
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,FContaminated lettuce leaves are
OL,17,Fbelieved to be the source of the
OL,18,Foutbreak, according to the Food
OL,19,FStandards Agency (FSA).
