OL,3,CDeath recorded in England linked to
OL,4,Congoing E.coli outbreak, UKHSA says
OL,6,FEarlier this month, a number of food
OL,7,Fmanufacturers recalled sandwiches,
OL,8,Fwraps and salads sold in major
OL,9,Fsupermarkets and retail chains over
OL,10,Ffears they are linked to the outbreak.
OL,12,FThe UKHSA said it had identified two
OL,13,Fpeople in England who died within 28
OL,14,Fdays of infection with shiga toxin-
OL,15,Fproducing E.coli (Stec).
OL,17,F"Based on the information available
OL,18,Ffrom health service clinicians one of
OL,19,Fthese deaths is likely linked to their
OL,20,FStec infection," it said.
