OL,3,CDeath recorded in England linked to
OL,4,Congoing E.coli outbreak, UKHSA says
OL,6,F"Both individuals had underlying
OL,7,Fmedical conditions. The deaths
OL,8,Foccurred in May."
OL,10,FAs of June 25, there have been a
OL,11,Ffurther 19 cases of Stec, bringing the
OL,12,Ftotal number of confirmed cases to 275
OL,13,Fin the UK.
OL,15,FThe UKHSA said the number of cases it
OL,16,Fis seeing is declining, but more will
OL,17,Fcome to light as further samples are
OL,18,Freferred from NHS laboratories.
