OL,4,Congoing E.coli outbreak, UKHSA says
OL,6,FTo this point, there have been 182
OL,7,Fcases in England, 58 in Scotland, 31
OL,8,Fin Wales and four in Northern Ireland.
OL,9,FThe latter cases are thought to have
OL,10,Facquired their infection in England.
OL,12,FAt least 122 people have been admitted
OL,13,Fto hospital for treatment since the
OL,14,Fstart of the outbreak.
