OL,3,CDeath recorded in England linked to
OL,4,Congoing E.coli outbreak, UKHSA says
OL,6,FDarren Whitby, head of incidents at
OL,7,Fthe FSA, said: "Earlier this month, we
OL,8,Fconfirmed that several sandwich
OL,9,Fmanufacturers had taken precautionary
OL,10,Faction to withdraw and recall various
OL,11,Fsandwiches, wraps, subs and rolls
OL,12,Fafter food chain and epidemiological
OL,13,Flinks enabled us to narrow down a wide
OL,14,Frange of foods to a type of lettuce
OL,15,Fused in sandwich products as the
OL,16,Flikely cause of the outbreak.
