OL,3,CDeath recorded in England linked to
OL,4,Congoing E.coli outbreak, UKHSA says
OL,6,F"This remains a complex investigation
OL,7,Fand we continue to work with the
OL,8,Frelevant businesses and the local
OL,9,Fauthorities to ensure necessary steps
OL,10,Fare being taken to protect consumers.
OL,12,F"Although we are confident in the
OL,13,Flikely source of the outbreak being
OL,14,Flinked to lettuce, work continues to
OL,15,Fconfirm this and identify the root
OL,16,Fcause of the outbreak with the
OL,17,Fgrowers, suppliers and manufacturers
OL,18,Fso that actions can be taken to
OL,19,Fprevent a re-occurrence."
